snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher is a charming, first-person, sandbox experience. You play as Beatrix LeBeau: a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the ‘Far, Far Range.’

Collect colorful slimes, grow crops, harvest resources, and explore the untamed wilds through the mastery of your all-purpose vacpack.

Slime Rancher is wiggling to PlayStation 4 this September!

Developed by Monomi Park
http://www.slimerancher.com
www.monomipark.com
